				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/C%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-thi/poem-v156h-D_IlDqgWMKRRkKiw">Cảm hoài thi - 感懷詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%A1p/C%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%ADnh-l%C3%A2u-ph%C3%BA/poem-FTw3BG-GzcqAD0laK1NgHw">Cần Chính lâu phú - 勤政樓賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%A1p/author-3lsm43EvROLW2MsmzDXkTg">Nguyễn Pháp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-Cao-M%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%A1c-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-x%C3%A3-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-qu%E1%BA%ADn-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n/poem-OHMF-SMTUy8SSs3daJWY0Q">Chân Định huyện, Cao Mại tổng, Bác Trạch xã Phạm quận công bi văn - 真定縣高邁總博澤社范郡公碑文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-ph%C3%B9ng-ng%C3%A3-phu/poem-vHlcedHAsQxrX7qyTPRWfA">Đạo phùng ngã phu - 道逢餓夫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-gia-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A1c/poem-w52NGg4k0na_rajDMu1bmg">Đắc gia thư, thị nhật tác - 得家書是日作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%E1%BB%87n-Thu%E1%BA%ADt/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tri-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%AD-ti%E1%BA%BFt/poem-4v9kRYaWHu6GmZ8c22UQKg">Điếu Nguyễn Tri Phương tử tiết - 悼阮知方死節</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%E1%BB%87n-Thu%E1%BA%ADt/author-yymqs1KI3fdivUUn-pVUSw">Nguyễn Thiện Thuật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-m%E1%BA%A1t-d%C4%A9-s%E1%BB%B1-chi-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%B4-H%E1%BB%93-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-ng%E1%BB%99-M%E1%BA%A1nh-V%C3%A2n-Khanh-ph%E1%BB%A5c-quy-L%C6%B0u-H%E1%BA%A1o-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C3%BAc-y%E1%BA%BFn-%E1%BA%A9m-t%C3%A1n/poem-rv9EJcr71JHZgPe06LZUgw">Đông mạt dĩ sự chi đông đô Hồ Thành đông ngộ Mạnh Vân Khanh, phục quy Lưu Hạo trạch túc yến, ẩm tán nhân vi tửu ca - 冬末以事之東都 湖城東遇孟雲卿，復歸劉顥宅宿宴，飲散因為醉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%E1%BA%ADt/L%E1%BB%AF-c%E1%BA%A3m-tam-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-m37m9hnQAlNzytoFl-RTuQ">Lữ cảm tam chương kỳ 2 - 旅感三章其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-g0-4Ou9M-64s36ucqZIoAQ">Lâm Bật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%C3%A1-Nam-nh%E1%BA%A1c-nh%E1%BA%ADp-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%93/poem-9myXxdyuGsX0zxdHRnQwXQ">Quá Nam nhạc nhập Động Đình hồ - 過南嶽入洞庭湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Gi%E1%BA%A3-c%C3%A1c-l%C3%A3o-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Nh%E1%BB%AF-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-wMiJs_Ug9qzG_gr6Vxvswg">Tống Giả các lão xuất Nhữ Châu - 送賈閣老出汝州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
